{"tid":975313,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"劉心悠呢張相真係超靚女","createTime":"2019-01-09T13:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T12:37:38.000Z","uid":54373,"like":11,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"27283c13035a37aa8712deeb1b7ea1adbca3fa99","tid":975313,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">劉心悠素顏現身機場</span><br />\n2014-10-01<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141001/large/01ec3p7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141001%2Flarge%2F01ec3p7e.jpg&h=fffe366d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉心悠現身機場，左避右避終於被迫面對鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n機場離境大堂昨日星光熠熠，除了謝霆鋒離境疑似會合王菲，劉嘉玲、陳慧琳（Kelly）、劉心悠及手抱囡囡的吳佩慈亦先後出現。一身潮look的Kelly中午12時多現身機場出埠工作，見到記者即笑着打招呼。而劉嘉則前往北京，是否會相約好姊妹王菲？嘉玲說要看時間。記者告知她霆鋒剛剛入閘離境，嘉玲則沒有回答，好友鄧霓儀亦隨嘉玲一同離港。<br />\n<br />\n昨日素顏的劉心悠遇見記者時有點愕然，更由南閘走到北閘避開記者拍照，未料兩邊閘口都有傳媒守候，最終都是難逃被影，問她去那兒？心悠則語帶無奈表示飛返台灣，但問她是否往探家人，則沒有回答。<br />\n<br />\n手抱囡囡出現的吳佩慈，昨日同樣是飛返台灣，但她為免囡囡容貌曝光，昨日全程遮住囡囡不讓大家拍攝。<br />\n採訪、攝影：溫敏芝、陳慧安"},{"pid":"3cfdab9de8affa4b7fa4de7eb94d23932a922aab","tid":975313,"uid":12000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"老雞"},{"pid":"ae41c5c341ba47053e26ac32dd215a9c47ba23db","tid":975313,"uid":54373,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/dvdgd_3695681675b14f1898f2cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fdvdgd_3695681675b14f1898f2cb.jpg&h=aedcdeef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcbbece0ae77d79ef3cc16e3a127189a32e500b0","tid":975313,"uid":16844,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:58:31.000Z","msg":"學好d廣東話先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22338475